{"tid":2260386,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"貨車司機天橋塗鴉「支持醫護罷工」、「毋忘沙士教訓」認刑毀 判囚2個月緩刑2年","createTime":"2020-10-27T13:54:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T00:54:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c69066f8758a245f198daf86fe5aa71e053c439a","tid":2260386,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:54:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10655\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F10655&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDCT1kznsNOvA2%2BdQC7BC3ts%3D&h=59419781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10655</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#羅德泉主任裁判官 <br />\n#提堂<br />\n#20200125荃灣<br />\n<br />\n劉(26)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：刑事損壞 ‼️認罪<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n被控於20年1月25日凌晨於荃灣港鐵站A出口外天橋用紅色噴漆噴字，包括「支持醫護罷工」、「毋忘沙士教訓」等。<br />\n<br />\n判刑：<br />\n起點定於三個月監禁，認罪扣減一個月，除此之外沒有其他減刑因素。<br />\n<br />\n法庭明言，於考慮此等刑事損壞案件時，法庭並非考慮內容誰是誰非，除非是非常特別的情況。<br />\n<br />\n判監兩個月，緩刑兩年，賠償$2,500予路政署。"},{"pid":"caa10471c21ca193c9057f9c57c1c13bdd335a1f","tid":2260386,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:55:51.000Z","msg":"緩刑兩年真係執到"},{"pid":"289291cd2b667a91795050e4b16217cd02ea0fb9","tid":2260386,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caa10471c21ca193c9057f9c57c1c13bdd335a1f","tid":2260386,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:55:51.000Z","msg":"緩刑兩年真係執到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:56:58.000Z","msg":"呢個官好似已經係蘇狗2.0嚟，咁都走得？"},{"pid":"92ebffc8cb8530f2e7c93940a7fcdddfedfbe2ad","tid":2260386,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece1dff262f2a4af8ae2f0dc7b79a94898535b9f","tid":2260386,"uid":136994,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"caa10471c21ca193c9057f9c57c1c13bdd335a1f","tid":